ockquote><br />\n二月去旅行都食唔切？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53dc4462dd9f5bb7239172339ed2af4d0182545","tid":476813,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:39:22.000Z","msg":"你依家都例遲,話唔定到2月果陣去哂成個旅行先黎呢<br />\n你依家咁快搞返準個M期到時再遲咪又係踩界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4360b5b45150ee3e308b9726170ee102f2a11be7","tid":476813,"uid":59559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"避孕丸咪得<br />\n又可以無限中出"},{"pid":"92d946f28e3c76183a6b7c763b3675c0851ecf71","tid":476813,"uid":83989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"你要延經點都影響個cycle㗎啦 黎住m去旅行有咩所謂其實"},{"pid":"8903f1385e337da16d57d333333a8bad4f98ebbe","tid":476813,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去藥房買藥食啦 旅行前幾日開始食 食到完旅行為止 d m就會黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前都試過睇醫生拎藥<br />\n但醫生話嗰d成份同事後丸一樣<br />\n仲要早2個禮拜食先有用<br />\n嗰陣已經食唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個啲係荷爾蒙藥黎喎 <br />\n我之前荷爾蒙失調婦科醫生都係開呢隻藥俾我 唔係事後藥 食咗藥都係要做足避孕措施"},{"pid":"98633115ef3e5fd8a70f0f4be52ac4a442889763","tid":476813,"uid":128904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:58:31.000Z","msg":"試過m之前三日開始食避孕藥(28粒嗰種)<br />\n食到去完旅行返黎(5日後)就停<br />\n過兩日就黎m<br />\n下個月黎m時間冇變 好正常<br />\n完全冇副作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇醫生攞避孕藥黎食根本就好安全<br />\n唔好去藥房亂買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有食紅棗etc嗰啲完全冇科學根據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你要信就隨便你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b946c41f06c0937ed394c2b0e0d43497aa78a3","tid":476813,"uid":51436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"好多巴打樂意幫你停10個月"},{"pid":"3be9d5f5f9d1d2d8f913594099c3e79f73efbe71","tid":476813,"uid":104256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:22:35.000Z","msg":"日日飲涼茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}